  "id": "RAW_a499e884",
  "title": "Anthropic 用一份报告，说透了 AI 时代的就业真相",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNTY1MjE2OA==&mid=2247493441&idx=1&sn=f545ea6859d55197b140d163d862c8e0",
  "date": "2026-03-09 11:26:00",
  "author": "乌鸦智能说",
  "siteName": "乌鸦智能说",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>硅基君</span> <span>2026-03-09 19:26</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">北京</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f1c5ca96&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F598Tr639EmPoDibQF9wJp516YGSXsaVZ0AT2eric3E5icQqaWV4JS5zpv2IUH9IibemMydreheagKBLRaoGqkXPA7mpNztACvymzQmSoXto8Pko%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>寻找个人的“非线性能力”</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/598Tr639EmMRMxCuYibK6jQzSSIVn68mrg4MfOI5ick7quiaQKJE4nvLwyFXqny91mvat54iaq1x0K9dvIG4G7XO4HQJjfSgho9pBFn2icJxluNg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"245\" data-imgfileid=\"100009786\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"width: 100%;pointer-events: initial;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2560\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5b88ac46&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F598Tr639EmMRMxCuYibK6jQzSSIVn68mrg4MfOI5ick7quiaQKJE4nvLwyFXqny91mvat54iaq1x0K9dvIG4G7XO4HQJjfSgho9pBFn2icJxluNg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: unset;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;caret-color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;line-height: 28px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 8.5px 17px;outline: 0px;line-height: 29.75px;min-height: 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(63, 63, 63);bottom: auto;float: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-width: 0px;top: auto;z-index: auto;visibility: visible;clear: none;background-image: none;background-color: rgb(235, 235, 235);background-size: auto;background-clip: border-box;background-position: 0% center;background-repeat: repeat;\">\n         <div>\n          <div>\n           <div>\n            <p><span leaf=\"\">最近，我看到了一篇非常硬核的研究报告。它像一面镜子，照出了当下AI 对就业市场最真实的冲击。</span></p>\n            <div>\n             <p><span leaf=\"\">读完之后感触很深，也想分享给各位读者。</span></p>\n             <p><span leaf=\"\">这份报告来自AI 公司 Anthropic，也就是知名模型 Claude 的开发者。报告由两位经济学研究员 Maxim Massenkoff 和 Peter McCrory 撰写。</span></p>\n             <p><span leaf=\"\">与许多停留在预测层面的研究不同，这份报告大量使用了真实的产品使用数据，试图回答一个非常现实的问题：AI正在如何改变我们的工作。</span></p>\n             <p><span leaf=\"\">整份研究看下来，给我最大的感觉是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">传统以人类智力为核心的线性生产曲线，正在被打破</span>。</span></p>\n             <p><span leaf=\"\">在过去几千年的历史里，人类的能力提升大致是线性的。</span></p>\n             <p><span leaf=\"\">这很好理解，一个人多读几年书，多积累几年经验，能力往往就会比别人强一点，相应地，收入和地位也会逐步提升。</span></p>\n             <p><span leaf=\"\">但AI 的出现，让社会的“智力密度分布”会变得更加陡峭。简单来说，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">人和人的差距又被拉大了</span>。</span></p>\n             <p><span leaf=\"\">一方面，AI会接管大量中等复杂度、以白领为核心的重复性脑力工作；另一方面，它又会极大地放大少数人的能力，让顶级个体获得前所未有的生产力提升。</span></p>\n             <p><span leaf=\"\">接下来，我们就从这个变化出发，具体展开聊聊。</span></p>\n            </div>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\">\n   <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 01 /</span></span></strong></span></strong></strong></span></strong></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">AI替代还在早期</span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">首先，我们得面对一个基本问题：AI到底能干多少活？</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">过去我们谈论AI替代率，往往是基于“理论能力”。比如某某研究说，大模型理论上能把这个任务的速度提升一倍。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">但这东西不能靠感觉，也不能只看理论。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">两位作者非常聪明地引入了一个新概念——“观测暴露度”（Observed Exposure）。</span></p>\n       <div>\n        <p><span leaf=\"\">这里的 “暴露度（Exposure）”，其实是劳动经济学里一个常用概念，可以理解为：某个职业“受到技术影响的程度”。</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">他们把美国O*NET数据库里的800多个职业任务，和Claude真实的后台使用数据（Anthropic Economic Index）做了一个交叉比对。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">结果一出来，非常有意思——AI远没有达到它的理论上限。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">数据显示，在Claude被用来完成的工作中，有97%确实属于理论上AI能胜任的范畴。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">但是，理论上能干，不代表现实中已经全覆盖了。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">以计算机和数学类岗位为例，理论上大模型能渗透其中94%的任务。但在现实中，Claude目前的实际覆盖率只有33%。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">原因有很多，模型本身的局限、法律合规约束、必须的人工验证步骤、特定软件要求……这些\"摩擦力\"在理论模型里是隐形的，但在现实中却是一堵堵高墙。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这说明什么？说明AI的渗透还在早期，我们还有喘息的窗口期。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">但别高兴得太早，真正的冲击，藏在那些已经被高强度覆盖的岗位里。</span></p>\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n           <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"10 5 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 02 /</span></span></span></strong></span></strong></p>\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">程序员最“受伤”</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">那到底是谁在被AI疯狂替代？</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">报告列出了“观测暴露度”最高的十大职业。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5464601769911505\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"904\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100009789\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=affd8537&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F598Tr639EmPneEv03z0ZBIAibU40ImBUr8y6WddVhggzbjwu60xPHVgTCiaozBBp83eCmzoqzYbqrDMLic1EENwDAk2c8MaBYLVSXdW8cfnOLY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">排在第一的，毫无悬念，是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">计算机程序员</span>，覆盖率高达75%。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">紧随其后的是客户服务代表，然后是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">数据录入员</span>（覆盖率67%）。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这非常符合直觉。写代码、回客服邮件、录入数据，这些高度结构化、基于文本的任务，恰恰是大模型最擅长的领域。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">而另一端呢？</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">有30%的打工人，他们的工作对AI的暴露度是零</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这些人是谁？厨师、摩托车修理工、救生员、调酒师、洗碗工……</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">如果你需要抡起袖子、流汗出力，或者需要面对面的人际互动，恭喜你，AI目前还动不了你的奶酪。</span></p>\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n           <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"10 5 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 03 /</span></span></span></strong></span></strong></p>\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">年轻人的“门”被关上了</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">看到这里，你可能会问：既然程序员、客服这么容易被AI覆盖，那他们是不是已经被大规模裁员了？</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这就是这份报告最让人后背发凉的地方——并没有。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">报告追踪了自2022年底（也就是ChatGPT发布）以来的失业率数据，发现那些高暴露度职业的失业率，并没有出现系统性的飙升。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">也就是说，公司并没有因为引入了AI，就把现有的程序员或客服大批开除。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">那冲击体现在哪里？</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">答案是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">年轻人找不到工作了</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">报告把目光对准了22到25岁的年轻打工人。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">数据揭示了一个残酷的现实：从2024年开始，年轻人在高暴露度职业中的就业率，出现了明显的下滑。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">相比于低暴露度职业稳定在每月2%的就业发现率，高暴露度职业的年轻血液正在干涸。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在后ChatGPT时代，这些高暴露度岗位的年轻人入职率，相比2022年下降了约14%。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这是一种极其隐蔽的“替代”。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">公司没有裁掉老员工，但他们关上了招聘新人的大门。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">老员工借助AI，一个人能干三个人的活。那为什么还要招那些需要培训、经验不足的新手呢？</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这就像温水煮青蛙，你不会在新闻里看到大规模的裁员潮，但年轻人的第一级职业阶梯，正在被悄无声息地抽走。</span></p>\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n           <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"10 5 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 04 /</span></span></span></strong></span></strong></p>\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">A</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">对白领群体的“精准打击”</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">更有意思的是，报告还刻画了这些高暴露度人群的画像。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">你以为容易被AI替代的都是低端劳动力？</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">错。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">数据显示，相比于那些对AI免疫的零暴露人群，高暴露度人群的画像是这样的：</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">女性比例高16个百分点，白人比例高11个百分点，亚裔比例几乎翻倍。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">最关键的是，他们受教育程度更高，赚得也更多。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.549889135254989\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"902\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100009788\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4212e46c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F598Tr639EmPtPBTagoVHxkXI1BuxicyBFqUtXfXJia3pqRmE7kZ42hicSZuZODV11xjZicjibqtzGtKA8CKrg0heY7CQVnPvRv5OmIxNMuHaHmDY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在最容易被AI冲击的群体中，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">拥有研究生学历的人占比高达17.4%，是未暴露组（4.5%）的近四倍！他们的平均收入也高出47%</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这是一场针对“白领精英”的精准打击。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">你寒窗苦读十几年，拿了高学历，坐在舒适的空调房里敲键盘、做表格、写报告。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">你以为你拿到的是铁饭碗，但AI告诉你：你干的这些，我不仅能干，而且干得比你快，还不要社保。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">如果未来发生一场“白领大衰退”，失业率翻倍，这份报告的框架已经做好了随时捕捉这一信号的准备。</span></p>\n       <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;\">\n         <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n          <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">\n           <div style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"10 5 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 19px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">/ 05 /</span></span></span></strong></span></strong></p>\n            <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;color: rgb(217, 33, 66);font-size: 17px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;font-family: \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 16px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;outline: 0px;line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);line-height: 1.75;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\">总结</span></strong></span></p>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">好了，冰冷的数据讲完了。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">回到开头那个问题：这篇像手术刀一样冷静的报告，对我们这些普通人，到底意味着什么？</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在过去几千年的历史里，人类的智力产出整体是相对线性的。简单说，你多读几年书、多积累几年经验，能力就会比别人强一点，收入和地位也会随之慢慢提高。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">但AI的到来，彻底打碎了这条线性曲线。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在接下来的几年里，我们将看到极其残酷的一幕：一方面，AI对中等智力进行粗暴的取代；另一方面，AI对高等智力进行恐怖的非线性赋能。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">结果就是，整个社会的“智力密度分布”会变得更加陡峭。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">理解了这个底层逻辑，无论是作为打工人还是投资者，你的决策路径就会变得极其清晰。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">作为个人，你必须去寻找属于自己的<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">“非线性能力”</span>。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在AI 时代，所有可重复生产的东西，价格都会快速下降。因为生产成本正在被技术压缩到极低。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">以绘画为例。过去，一幅精美的插画需要多年训练和数小时创作。但现在，像Midjourney 这样的工具，普通人十分钟就可以生成一张高质量作品。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">当创作工具完全普及之后，单纯依赖“技术门槛”的价值体系就会被迅速削弱。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">真正变得稀缺的，反而是那些难以复制的东西，比如审美判断、个人风格、叙事能力、情感连接。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，在AI 时代，当生产力趋近于无限时，价值并不会消失，而是会迁移。它会从“事物本身”，转移到“事物背后的意义”。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">这个逻辑其实很像F1比赛。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">在这项赛事里，最有价值的资产不是赛车，而是车手。因为赛车的性能相对稳定，但驾驶员的判断力和技能差异很大，车手才是影响比赛结果的最大变量。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">人工智能也是一样。强大的工具在不同的人手里，会产生完全不同的结果。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">归根结底，AI带来的并不是简单的替代，而是一次生产力结构的重排。</span></p>\n       <p><span leaf=\"\">如何确保在AI推进的过程中不被时代抛弃，是我们每个人都要严肃思考的命题。</span></p>\n       <p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(63, 63, 63);color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: italic;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 1px;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration: none;float: none;display: inline !important;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\">文/林白</span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;\"><em style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">PS：</span></em></span><em style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 14px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你也在寻找投资AI资产的机会，欢迎扫码加入我们的交流群。</span></em></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: unset;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4154676258992806\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2224\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: center;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);visibility: visible !important;width: 657px !important;height: auto !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/598Tr639EmPXqeIt1JxGObLJE7cTIRS5j8xgB4pQibxP9NMa5VAaa4pcDmlPNFv3smXpWTxBHbgqGyN3Yj4IALyd4wUWbGPfU3icCF2oxqpD0/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"558\" data-cropsely2=\"232\" data-imgfileid=\"100009774\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8333c4e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F598Tr639EmPXqeIt1JxGObLJE7cTIRS5j8xgB4pQibxP9NMa5VAaa4pcDmlPNFv3smXpWTxBHbgqGyN3Yj4IALyd4wUWbGPfU3icCF2oxqpD0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n  <p><a href=\"%27%27\">阅读原文</a></p>\n  <p><a href=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/link-proxy/?k=91596d4a&amp;r=1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%3F__biz%3DMzkyNTY1MjE2OA%3D%3D%26mid%3D2247493441%26idx%3D1%26sn%3Df545ea6859d55197b140d163d862c8e0\">跳转微信打开</a></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文深度解读了 Anthropic 关于 AI 对就业市场影响的研究报告，指出 AI 正在通过减少新人招聘而非直接裁员的方式，精准冲击高学历白领群体。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文深度解读了 Anthropic 关于 AI 对就业市场影响的研究报告，指出 AI 正在通过减少新人招聘而非直接裁员的方式，精准冲击高学历白领群体。",
  "summary": "文章基于 Anthropic 发布的最新经济研究报告，分析了 AI 对职场的真实冲击。研究引入了“观测暴露度”这一核心概念，发现虽然 AI 在理论上能胜任大量任务，但受限于法律、合规及人工验证等“摩擦力”，实际渗透率仍处于早期阶段。报告揭示了一个残酷的现实：AI 的冲击并非表现为大规模裁员，而是通过提高老员工效率来缩减新人招聘，导致 22-25 岁年轻人的入职率显著下降。受影响最严重的群体并非低端劳动力，而是高学历、高收入的白领精英。作者最后建议，在智力密度分布日益陡峭的 AI 时代，个人应寻求审美判断、叙事能力等“非线性能力”以维持竞争价值。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 的实际应用远未达到理论上限，渗透仍处早期。",
      "explanation": "通过对比 Claude 真实后台数据与职业任务，发现法律、合规及人工验证等现实“摩擦力”阻碍了 AI 的全面覆盖，为人类留下了窗口期。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 对就业的冲击体现为“隐形替代”，即关上招聘大门。",
      "explanation": "企业并未大规模裁减老员工，而是利用 AI 提升现有人员产出，从而显著减少了对 22-25 岁年轻新人的需求，入职率下降约 14%。"
    },
    {
      "point": "高学历白领精英是 AI 暴露度最高、最易受冲击的群体。",
      "explanation": "研究发现高暴露人群中研究生学历占比是未暴露组的近四倍，AI 正在精准打击那些依赖结构化脑力劳动的传统精英岗位。"
    },
    {
      "point": "个人价值将从“事物本身”迁移到“事物背后的意义”。",
      "explanation": "在生产力趋于无限的时代，单纯的技术门槛将被削弱，审美判断、个人风格和情感连接等难以复制的非线性能力将成为核心竞争力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 远没有达到它的理论上限……这些‘摩擦力’在理论模型里是隐形的，但在现实中却是一堵堵高墙。",
    "公司没有裁掉老员工，但他们关上了招聘新人的大门。年轻人的第一级职业阶梯，正在被悄无声息地抽走。",
    "这是一场针对‘白领精英’的精准打击。你以为你拿到的是铁饭碗，但 AI 告诉你：你干的这些，我不仅能干，而且干得比你快。",
    "在 AI 时代，当生产力趋近于无限时，价值并不会消失，而是会迁移。它会从‘事物本身’，转移到‘事物背后的意义’。"
